{"tid":164014,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺火影忍者賞析可以成為大學course?","createTime":"2017-03-20T11:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T19:29:18.000Z","uid":86587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf3a9d4f97c1aa7f55351a22dc79f26934d1107","tid":164014,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:38:16.000Z","msg":"火影忍者漫畫入門賞析 Introduction to the Appreciation of Naruto Manga<br />\n<br />\n報讀課程既學生需要滿足CRCW要求，需要睇哂成本火影漫畫以及相關journal去完成term paper <br />\n<br />\nTest 1(week 7, 90 min, 30%)<br />\n50條mc，頭40條考基本火影知識<br />\n之後10條考冷門知識<br />\n<br />\nTest2(week 13, 120 min, 30%)<br />\n兩題長答<br />\n問1:宇智波慘劇係木葉高層定宇智波本身造成<br />\n問2:火影邊個提出通往和平既方法最有效可行？試比較及解釋<br />\n<br />\nTerm paper(40%, max 3500字)<br />\n解釋火影忍術同建築與日本傳統文化嘅關係 (引用圖片數量不限，唯範圍限於火影漫畫本身，subheading max 8個)<br />\n交兩次draft: <br />\ndraft 1(week 6, 唔計分，由中文centre提出相關改善建議）<br />\ndraft 2(week10, 10%, 由中文centre就表達同組織評分)<br />\nFinal work(week 13, 30%)<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人幫手諗schedule同syllabus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900767429a2cf26ad5a5205c9714f48538bf703b","tid":164014,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"辣殺漫畫<br />\n小學生就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd4ad946bdd0c93ef7246cc1c5b18a77b209431","tid":164014,"uid":29549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"Group Project：2-4人一組，自選任何小隊形式的忍者進行角色扮演，並部析其人物的性格特點"},{"pid":"ce910b2b7a82b62a703f5edbfed71c1475bae500","tid":164014,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T12:35:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辣殺漫畫<br />\n小學生就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2fb5facb24898459a43e82d946d67345a3e3c06","tid":164014,"u